<!--
  - For deployment of reporting:
  -
  - Local development:
  -   ** Quick for writing AsciiDoctor **
  -   mvn -P site-author -pl ':parent' site
  -   ** With aggregation for javadoc/jxr **
  -   mvn -P site-author -pl ':parent,junit5' -Dskip.aggregate=false site
  -
  - Local build:
  -   ** Executes site:stage after building every modules **
  -   mvn -P gh-pages clean site site:stage
  -
  - Deploy to Github "gh-pages":
  -   mvn -P gh-pages -pl ":parent" scm-publish:publish-scm
  -
  - Properties:
  - 	-Dscmpublish.dryRun=true (Make the job dry run)
  -
  - For deployment of artifacts(to OSSRH):
  -
  -   mvn -P oss-deploy -DskipTests=true deploy
  -->
